### Successful meme generation (replace image path with a real file on your machine)
# NOTE: Do NOT set `Content-Type` manually — clients (VS Code REST Client or curl) must set the multipart boundary.
# For the VS Code REST Client, use the file attachment syntax shown below (update the path):
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/meme-generation

@image=@D:/meme-generator/backend/tests/sample.jpg;type=image/jpeg
text=Hello from tests.http - giữ nguyên ý nghĩa, làm ngắn gọn
font_size=48
color=white
position=bottom

